*glpng-1.46 (24 Mar 2015)

  24 Mar 2015; James Le Cuirot <chewi@gentoo.org> +glpng-1.46.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Version bump. I'm taking over this package as I have upstream commit access.
  Closes bug #332511 (CVE-2010-1519).

  12 Oct 2012; Michael Sterrett <mr_bones_@gentoo.org> glpng-1.45-r1.ebuild:
  add virtual/glu dep (bug #438128)

  09 Aug 2011; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org> glpng-1.45-r1.ebuild,
  +files/glpng-1.45-libpng15.patch:
  Fix building with libpng15 wrt #378417 by Diego Elio Pettenò

  31 May 2011; Tomáš Chvátal <scarabeus@gentoo.org> glpng-1.45-r1.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Move to eapi4 and drop wrong dep. Drop maintainership as i no longer use it
  in my projects.

  15 Jan 2011; Brent Baude <ranger@gentoo.org> glpng-1.45-r1.ebuild:
